{"tid":1469372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入中國領空被拒 國泰返港機迫降日本","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:37:09.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef30b1a5703f0a3a2c13fef2aef8d33fa16c305","tid":1469372,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:36:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%98%E7%A9%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%BF%94%E6%B8%AF%E6%A9%9F%E8%BF%AB%E9%99%8D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-214500838.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A0%2598%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E8%25BF%2594%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E9%2599%258D%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-214500838.html&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0RVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=95ef2f96\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%98%E7%A9%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%BF%94%E6%B8%AF%E6%A9%9F%E8%BF%AB%E9%99%8D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-214500838.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z.ikBQB7Ti37ISghILj5Lw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/72e10bab677ae407dc6ec0f0e5197a06\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fz.ikBQB7Ti37ISghILj5Lw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F72e10bab677ae407dc6ec0f0e5197a06&h=d023d47c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國泰CX899航機繞道俄羅斯在日本關西機場降落。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在中國民航局加強審批國泰航空機組人員資料之際，一班原定由美國紐瓦克回港的國泰航班CX899，本周日起飛後未有按原定路線經過中國領空回港，反而繞道俄羅斯並在日本關西機場降落，引起外界關注國泰是否未有提交此班航班的機組人員資料。不過，國泰回覆查詢時表示，有向內地當局提交機組人員資料，又稱該班為不載客航班，轉飛至大阪是為減輕香港機場負擔。<br />\n<br />\n稱未載客 兜路減港機場負擔<br />\n<br />\n根據飛行網站FlightAware的資料，該班CX899航班以往會由美國經中國領空飛抵香港，但在周日、即中國民航局要求國泰提交機組人員資料首日，該班機沒有使用一貫航道，反而繞道俄羅斯並在日本關西機場降落。根據《中國長安網》報道，國泰因未提交CX899航班的機組人員名單，未獲批進入中國領空，航班顯示為「空飛」。<br />\n<br />\n國泰發言人表示，由於香港國際機場在前日實施航空交通管制，航空交通擁擠，有見不少長途航班正接近香港國際機場途中，為盡量減低對乘客的不便，因此國泰安排由美國紐瓦克前往香港的不載客航班CX899，轉飛至大阪，減輕機場負擔，並讓其他載客航班先行回港。<br />\n<br />\n但大公唔係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6f5a25573d3dbb5cad3e1b85078cfcb48125bc","tid":1469372,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:37:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}